  "texts": [
    "The issue of factual inaccuracy in LLMs is a pressing concern that necessitates innovative solutions.",
    "The integration of RAG represents a promising avenue for enhancing the factual accuracy of LLMs.",
    "Through the detailed examination of the implementation and evaluation of RAG-augmented Llama, this paper seeks to contribute to the ongoing efforts to improve the reliability and trustworthiness of LLMs in various applications.Achieving higher factual accuracy in LLMs is of considerable significance for several reasons.",
    "First, as LLMs are increasingly integrated into decision-making processes, misinformation generated by these models can have serious real-world implications.",
    "For example, in the medical field, inaccurate information can lead to incorrect diagnoses or treatment recommendations, potentially endangering lives."
